track_notes: Round-trip, High Point Trailhead, West Tiger #3 Trail, continues and joins maintenance road, ending at West Tiger #1 summit (SOTA site) at locked gate and hikers hut. Suggest continuing to back-side of activation zone via Poo Top and Preston Trail. Return trip takes TMT Connector and Tiger Mtn Trail to return to West Tiger #3 Trail.
track_title: Round-trip, High Point Trailhead to West Tiger 1 SOTA site
